{"tid":2172940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港匯強勁！金管局承接美元沽盤　向市場注入逾6億港元","createTime":"2020-08-25T03:07:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T03:53:27.000Z","uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2ec2587c1c5a51f235fdae268ee4909e2605bd10","tid":2172940,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:07:55.000Z","msg":"港元匯價觸及1美元兌7.75港元強方兌換保證，是3周以來首次。<br />\n<br />\n金管局在紐約時段承接美元沽盤，沽出6.43億港元，令明日本港銀行體系總結餘增加至1883.83億港元，創近3年高位。<br />\n<br />\n外電數據顯示，自今年4月以來，港匯強方兌換被觸發超過30次，累計大約有1133億港元資金流入港元體系。<br />\nRTHK"},{"pid":"d50092488fbd7b2a51fd0238d48ff62909edd4d7","tid":2172940,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:11:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黎哂抽新股"},{"pid":"f7ebbfac353e6ea0db602e22f7016b253e65393d","tid":2172940,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:14:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024cd0936f251dc1ecbf3f58e364f85763109464","tid":2172940,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:17:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb232d7f9134b875990b11349d75df09754d266d","tid":2172940,"uid":123562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:18:30.000Z","msg":"驚係美國冇得買 啲錢流曬入香港買中資嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7459c3c7d729bef7f9b4d7dd8a64e1a08179c73f","tid":2172940,"uid":191926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:19:44.000Z","msg":"幾多中概股  走緊返來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港匯要轉弱 <br />\n關鍵係美國開始對付蘇聯咁  <br />\n斬斷中國金流<br />\n<br />\n禁止聯邦僱邦僱員基金，教育基金<br />\n直接/間接持有 <br />\n中國企業股票，債券係第一步<br />\n(包括恆大果堆高息債)<br />\n<br />\n因為班華爾街陷家鏟阻住<br />\n暫時都係只聞樓梯響<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49419f532dcf726e8fdd794a56d53e2fa87810dc","tid":2172940,"uid":64874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:53:27.000Z","msg":"除咗買實體貴金屬，咁香港人都可以趁呢水去唱做美元泊住先，呢排美元弱，直接唱其他外幣好蝕底。遲吓班人以為chinaden贏美元轉強，先轉埋做其他外幣。"}]}